title: Anna Calvi "Love Of My Life" : Converse EMPTY SPACE #5
description:
The 5th opus of EMPTY SPACE series has seen English artist Anna Calvi delivering a breathtaking performance in the royal castle of Fontainebleau.
An incredible interpretation of 'Love Of My Life' in front of a public of statues and hunting trophies.
